${goto 5}${voffset 5}${color}${font Noto:normal:size=10}C1: ${color2}${cpu cpu1}%${goto 70}${color1}${freq 1}Mhz${color}${goto 155}C2: ${color2}${cpu cpu2}%${goto 218}${color1}${freq 2}Mhz
